.IP
Project homepage. Accessible through {{homepage}} variable.
.HP
\fB\-\-license\fR[=\fI\,\/\fR]<identifier>
.IP
Author's homepage. Accessible through {{license}} variable.
.HP
\fB\-\-name\fR[=\fI\,\/\fR]<name>
.IP
